# release-bot: restart after changes

When you finish edits that affect runtime behavior (TypeScript under `src/`, `agent.ts`, `.env`, `package.json`, or PM2-related scripts), **in the same turn**:

1. From the project root run: `pnpm run restart:env`
2. Confirm: `curl -fsS http://127.0.0.1:8787/health` returns `{"ok":true,...}`

If PM2 is not used in the environment, say so instead of failing silently.
